Name: Magical Stock Princess
About the game: MAGICAL STOCK PRINCESS Gulamesh the Devourer has returned and he is stealing all the food, thus starving the people of the Kingdom. Princess Stock sets on a quest to collect as much food as possible and ultimately defeat Gulamesh! Magical Stock Princess is a quick to play blend of arcade levels and lite rpg elements. Avoid monsters while you clear the floor in the Gals Panic-loosely inspired Action stages, and interact with quirky characters in the Adventure stages. Enjoy the best of two worlds without the drawbacks. 100% bat caves-free. FEATURES: - A mix of arcade action and rpg elements. - A miniquest-based saving system. Saving doesn't come free, you need to work for it. - 3 endings plus a special bad ending. - Secrets, not the usual references and a lighthearted atmosphere. - Delicious food to collect! PLAY IT TODAY! Presented by IFCATS
